.DT
set_script_data_location
Disk World creator help
set_script_data_location

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_script_data_location -  This method replaces the script data at the specified location in the script with a new item.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_script_data_location(string name,
int pos,
class script_data data)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the script name
%^BOLD%^pos%^RESET%^ - the position to replace
%^BOLD%^data%^RESET%^ - the data to replace it with
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/scripting.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method replaces the script data at the specified location in
the script with a new item.
.EP

